      • updateShoppingCart

        void updateShoppingCart(products.Product product,
                        java.lang.String operation)
        Updates the shopping Cart adding or removing products from it
        Parameters:
        product - : Element to be added/removed from the cart
        operation - : either add or remove from the cart. If operation = [Delete] then the item is removed from the cart; if operation = [Insert] the item is added to the cart
